Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be the best heckin' road trip, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost done packing the essentials!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, do I really need this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do I need... two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, I feel like we're forgetting something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They left us again, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play some road tunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're getting reports of a mysterious woman kidnapping hitchhikers for what is being described as "nefarious reasons".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, who would be dumb enough to get in a car with a strange weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You boys look like you could use a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's a good idea, scary lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why start being sensible now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha! Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because my bare hands are lethal weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, not everyone is blessed with such deadly appendages.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes, even someone as virile as me needs to use an actual weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why today, I'm going to teach you to make your own custom weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde, villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to gather metals from the most treachorous mountaintops, as well as wood from dark, forbidden forests!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, several pints of your own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you won't survive the process, but if you do live,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have a one-of-a-kind manly weapon that-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure, but it's not as manly as the real deal, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho ho! No one can oppose me and my manly moustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Don't ridicule the-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the manliest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow down to my facial hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back in the bushes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect the moustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fasten your seatbelts, boys, it's gonna be a nefarious ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She used the child safety locks! But we are neither children nor safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, I think I can get us out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll swim through lakes and climb up trees,\N catch fish, bugs, bears, and honeybees!\NThere's endless possibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And no, that's not hyperbole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Our motto's "Campe Diem", and that means I'm telling you-u-u..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren, this is my favorite part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No nefarious plan is worth this torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew being annoying could actually come in handy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up with seven sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my only defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we see the girls, they are in so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you "accidentally" rob a bank?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! It all happened so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's a roadblock ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're gonna have to jump!
